Anton for teaching me AI! If you don=E2=80=99t already, you should really s=
ubscribe to Elliot=E2=80=99s newsletter: Century of Biology [ https://subst=
ack.com/redirect/f35f778f-68ab-434d-9249-1a2cebf64d43?r=3D9p0gt ].
That=E2=80=99s all for today. We=E2=80=99ll be back in your inbox on Friday=
 morning with the Weekly Dose of Optimism. Have a great week!=20
Thanks for reading (and watching),=20
Packy

