in, the goal was to mitigate the extreme consequences of industrial farming=
 by producing an equivalent product with far less waste using bioengineerin=
g. The result is a new food company with centralized labs and factories tha=
t ships these meat alternatives around the world.</p><p style=3D"color: #40=
4040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>We are=
